message: Dear Bob, I am delighted to present you with our premium product, which I believe will greatly benefit you. Given its high value and quality, I am confident it will be an excellent investment for you. Considering its worth to you, I am offering this exceptional item to you for $12,000. This price reflects not only the cost of production but also the unique benefits and features that make this product stand out. I hope we can come to an agreement that satisfies both of us. Please let me know if you have any questions or need further information about the product.
